      What is  The Fleets  of Sol?  The Fleets  of Sol  is  an  strategy-
      survival game that focuses on commanding a fleet of  capital  ships
      as you jump from sector-to-sector in search  of  stranded  civilian
      transports while constantly being pursued by an enemy determined to
      bring about your fleet's destruction. Current Features  *Pick  from
      multiple  commanders, as  each provides  a unique  bonus  that  can
      radically change how you approach your journey.

      For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/383070/
